A new stokvel has set WhatsApp abuzz. Courtesy #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - A new stokvel has set WhatsApp abuzz. The stokvel titled, Whatsapp Gifting, bears the hallmarks of a pyramid scheme. WATCH: Association warns of WhatsApp stokvel Participants are urged to invest a minimum of R200, which is said to earn big profits within days. Last year, a similar stokvel, failed after only a couple of months. Andrew Lukhele from the National Stokvel Association of South Africa has warned against such schemes. Watch the video above for more on this story.